<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="I" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Illumine" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Illumine,</orth> the same: <cit><quote>so is her face --d with her eye,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 486" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 486</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>fostered, --d, cherished,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.1.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 1, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>it --th the face,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.3.116" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B IV, 3, 116</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>illuminateth</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>